Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.76,0:22:09.76,sign_31763_303_Strelizia_Apath,Sign,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fs40\fsp20\pos(1292,903)}鹤望兰
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.76,0:22:13.18,Default,ViceChief,0,0,0,,鹤望兰拒绝了一切的干涉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.18,0:22:16.27,Default,Chief,0,0,0,,也就是说她干掉了我们的程序？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.85,0:22:22.77,Default,Z2,0,0,0,,{\blur5}现在我感觉你比何时都离我更近
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.19,0:22:26.61,Default,Z2,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你所想的事情　我都能清清楚楚地明白
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.57,0:22:30.20,Default,Z2,0,0,0,,{\blur5}从今往后　无论发生什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.20,0:22:33.45,Default,Z2,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我们的心永远在一起　Darling！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.52,0:22:58.94,Default,Fra,0,0,0,,看到了　我看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.94,0:23:02.27,Default,Fra,0,0,0,,啊　多么美丽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.27,0:23:04.27,Default,Fra,0,0,0,,我的天燕座
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.82,0:23:08.03,Default,Fra,0,0,0,,鹤望兰·天燕座！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.20,0:23:17.12,Default,ViceChief,0,0,0,,那就没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.12,0:23:20.29,Default,ViceChief,0,0,0,,由叫龙制成的生命之枪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.29,0:23:24.67,Default,ViceChief,0,0,0,,虽说我们想要的不止这些　但我们就先这样暂时撤退吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.14,0:23:36.18,Default,ViceChief,0,0,0,,但是我们会再次来临
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.18,0:23:40.19,Default,ViceChief,0,0,0,,那时候我们会带着全部兵力{Flag}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.19,0:23:42.19,Default,ViceChief,0,0,0,,将这颗星球消灭掉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.15,0:23:44.27,Default,9a,0,0,0,,爸爸...
